Publisher's Description▼▲
When an artist creates a great work, he typically finds a place to put his signature, so everyone will know he did it. Did God do something similar when he created life? Join us with Dr. Stephen Meyer, author of the book Signature in the Cell which is opening eyes and changing minds on the question of origins. Hear how the hard evidence of science is bringing materialistic evolution into question in a whole new way.


