bummed





 






1 Stars Out Of 5



Not what I expected


June 28, 2016



bummed






  

Quality:




4
 
Value:




1
 
Meets Expectations:




1
  
            The product description of this product is incomplete or inaccurate.  This is NOT an audio version of the text of the book Signature in the Cell.  Rather, this is an audio recording of a program during which they discussed the book Signature in the Cell.  As I recall, I think it was about an hour long radio program.  If you purchase this looking for the actual book, you will be disappointed, as I was.
        














