Product & Solutions for Head & Neck Treatment Areas
Whether it's muscle strains, whiplash or herniated discs, you'll find treatment supplies to help alleviate head and neck pain at Meyer Physical Therapy. Utilize portable traction systems, posture straps, neck contours, topical pain relievers and other supplies to treat, rehabilitate and prevent pain and irritation associated with head and neck pain. Choose from a variety of current head and neck treatment solutions.   
	LEARN MORE






 
Product & Solutions for Shoulder Treatment Areas
Whether it's everyday wear and tear, instability or a torn rotator cuff, you can rest assured your patients will have access to the best supplies and equipment on the market for treating shoulder injuries. Find quality supports, compression wraps, pulley systems and more. At Meyer Physical Therapy, shoulder treatment has never been easier.  
	LEARN MORE






 
Product & Solutions for Back Treatment Areas
Yard work, heavy lifting and excessive twistingand simply getting olderare all things that have the potential to flood your practice with cases of minor to severe back injuries. At Meyer Physical Therapy, you'll find a large variety of quality treatment products that will assist you in supplying patients with the proper equipment, exercise methods and treatment solutions for individual back pain needs.  
	LEARN MORE






 
Product & Solutions for Knee Treatment Areas
Complex in design and actively weight-bearing, the knee is one of the most commonly injured joints in the body. From treatment for sprains and strains to dislocations and ligament tears, Meyer Physical Therapy has the supplies you need to treat, rehabilitate and prevent injuries in the knee. Choose from quality compression sleeves, braces, straps and more to help relieve irritation and eliminate inflammation. Updated therapeutic practices and treatment solutions will help you promote increased mobility and restore confidence among patients. Find your knee treatment area supplies today.  
	LEARN MORE






 
Product & Solutions for Arm & Elbow Treatment Areas
Tendinitis, tennis elbow and carpal tunnel syndrome will be a thing of the past with our selection of treatment solutions at Meyer Physical Therapy. Use specialized cold compression wraps, braces, splints and other quality materials and equipment to assist you in the treatment, rehabilitation and/or prevention of symptoms associated with various types of arm and elbow injury. Locate the supplies you need today.  
	LEARN MORE






 
Product & Solutions for Wrist & Hand Treatment Areas
					A minor hand and/or wrist injury is nearly a universal experiencealmost everyone has endured one at some point. Let us help you find the proper support solution for fingers, thumbs and wrists in both functional and resting positions. From treatment for thumb sprains to scaphoid fractures, you'll find the supplies you need to treat and prevent wrist and hand injuries at Meyer Physical Therapy.  
	LEARN MORE






 
Product & Solutions for Hip & Pelvic Treatment Areas
Provide relief from hip and pelvic injuries with effective treatment solutions from Meyer Physical Therapy. From industrial support belts to molded foam ring cushions, you'll find the supplies you need to successfully assist patients through the rehabilitation process.  
	LEARN MORE






 
Product & Solutions for Abdominal & Torso Treatment Areas
Help patients target abdominal pain and promote improved torso stabilization. At Meyer Physical Therapy, you'll find a vast assortment of products, such as lumbosacral supports and exercise equipment for stabilizing abdominal muscles and improving core strength. Turn to us for the latest trends and product selection in abdominal care, so you can promote proper posture and contribute to pain relief in patients with weak abdomens and torsos.  
	LEARN MORE






 
Product & Solutions for Ankle & Foot Treatment Areas
No matter if it's a sprain, strain or fracture, you can find the proper ankle support, brace or walker to help patients get back to an active lifestyle, all in one place. At Meyer Physical Therapy, you'll find a wide range of quality products for treating chronic pain or injuries in the ankle and foot. We pride ourselves on providing all the latest treatment tools, so you and your patients can stay at the top of your game.  
	LEARN MORE






