 COMPANY





Our Commitment to Service
Meyer Physical Therapy is a leading supplier of therapy, rehabilitation, and health & wellness supplies and equipment with a broad selection of high quality, brand name products and product knowledge. Passionate about helping you care for your patients, our attentive and knowledgeable sales representative and customer service teams are always available to assist you with competitive pricing, fast delivery and insight into the newest products and latest industry trends. Whether evaluating and treating your patients in a private practice, home, hospital or other type of health care setting, we want to supply you with the proper products and essential information you need to restore an improved quality of life.





